1
00:00:14,556 --> 00:00:16,266
Are you coming home late today?

2
00:00:16,266 --> 00:00:18,101
He might not go home at all.

3
00:00:18,101 --> 00:00:18,893
Who is this?

4
00:00:18,893 --> 00:00:22,022
And why do you have Seo Yujun's phone?

5
00:00:24,274 --> 00:00:27,318
Someone who wants to take...

6
00:00:29,487 --> 00:00:32,032
...Seo Yujun away from you.

7
00:01:00,602 --> 00:01:03,438
Yujun.

8
00:01:03,438 --> 00:01:05,190
Why did you drink so much?

9
00:01:05,190 --> 00:01:06,191
Hmm?

10
00:01:07,609 --> 00:01:09,444
He didn't want to go home.

11
00:01:09,444 --> 00:01:10,945
I guess there's someone he doesn't want to see...

12
00:01:10,945 --> 00:01:12,864
...waiting for him there.

13
00:01:13,114 --> 00:01:18,119
Even so, you should've sent a drunk person home.

14
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:25,001
Let's go, Yujun.

15
00:01:25,001 --> 00:01:28,088
I'm planning to seriously make a move on Yujun this time.

16
00:01:29,923 --> 00:01:31,758
I've actually liked him for a long time.

17
00:01:32,050 --> 00:01:34,677
Yujun's heart won't change that easily.

18
00:01:36,471 --> 00:01:37,764
Well...

19
00:01:37,764 --> 00:01:39,557
I guess...

20
00:01:42,936 --> 00:01:44,521
We'll just have to wait and see.

21
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:49,150
Let's go.

22
00:02:28,148 --> 00:02:29,691
How's your stomach?

23
00:02:33,862 --> 00:02:35,738
Just a headache, but I'm fine.

24
00:02:37,407 --> 00:02:40,577
By the way, how did I get home last night?

25
00:02:41,202 --> 00:02:43,746
You found your way back fine.

26
00:02:45,165 --> 00:02:46,499
By myself?

27
00:02:46,791 --> 00:02:48,168
Yeah.

28
00:02:50,086 --> 00:02:52,005
That's a relief.

29
00:02:52,005 --> 00:02:54,090
I was worried I might have bothered you.

30
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,514
Sleep a little more.

31
00:03:01,514 --> 00:03:03,391
I'll wake you up when I leave.

32
00:03:03,391 --> 00:03:04,350
Okay?

33
00:03:04,684 --> 00:03:05,643
Okay.

34
00:03:18,406 --> 00:03:20,033
You are my whole world...

35
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:21,242
...and my everything.

36
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:26,080
I can't even imagine you leaving me.

37
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,124
I will take responsibility for you forever.

38
00:03:28,124 --> 00:03:30,084
I'll keep you by my side and never let you go.

39
00:03:30,084 --> 00:03:32,503
So...

40
00:03:32,795 --> 00:03:38,426
Can't you just love everything I do for you?

41
00:03:50,897 --> 00:03:54,484
I think he said these were his thesis materials.

42
00:04:07,205 --> 00:04:08,957
Thanks for drinking with me yesterday.

43
00:04:10,708 --> 00:04:13,127
I don't even remember how I got home.

44
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:18,132
I had fun too.

45
00:04:19,634 --> 00:04:23,263
But did you completely black out yesterday?

46
00:04:26,182 --> 00:04:27,350
Yes.

47
00:04:27,976 --> 00:04:30,436
I think I was rambling, but...

48
00:04:30,436 --> 00:04:32,855
I didn't say anything weird, did I?

49
00:04:41,072 --> 00:04:42,907
Why are you looking at me like that?

50
00:04:42,907 --> 00:04:44,325
Did I really say something...

51
00:04:44,325 --> 00:04:46,202
So you don't remember my confession either?

52
00:04:47,078 --> 00:04:48,037
What?

53
00:04:49,455 --> 00:04:51,165
I confessed my feelings to you yesterday.

54
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:55,336
If someone who does too much for you is overwhelming...

55
00:04:55,336 --> 00:04:57,338
...then you should date someone moderate like me.

56
00:04:58,298 --> 00:04:59,799
Hyunseo sunbae...

57
00:05:01,592 --> 00:05:02,802
Yujun.

58
00:05:05,138 --> 00:05:07,056
I like you.

59
00:05:09,058 --> 00:05:12,562
Since there was no place for me by your side...

60
00:05:12,562 --> 00:05:15,606
...I thought this would just be a one-sided love I'd have to end alone.

61
00:05:16,816 --> 00:05:18,818
But it looks like I finally have a chance now.

62
00:05:21,863 --> 00:05:23,906
Do you want to use me?

63
00:05:24,198 --> 00:05:25,742
What do you mean, use you?

64
00:05:44,886 --> 00:05:47,221
If you want to break up with him, use me all you want.

65
00:05:48,973 --> 00:05:52,518
If that's what it takes to take the spot beside you...

66
00:05:52,518 --> 00:05:54,645
...then I'm completely satisfied with that.

67
00:06:38,189 --> 00:06:40,066
You don't have to cook.

68
00:06:41,692 --> 00:06:42,944
Did you already eat?

69
00:06:43,277 --> 00:06:44,529
Yeah.

70
00:06:44,529 --> 00:06:45,947
My professor bought me dinner.

71
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,992
I can just eat by myself then.

72
00:06:50,701 --> 00:06:51,744
What about your mother?

73
00:06:55,289 --> 00:06:56,999
Have you talked to her lately?

74
00:06:57,708 --> 00:06:59,210
Why bring up my mother all of a sudden?

75
00:07:02,588 --> 00:07:03,923
Why?

76
00:07:03,923 --> 00:07:06,217
Do you want to go and formally greet her together?

77
00:07:09,053 --> 00:07:11,305
No, Mom.

78
00:07:11,305 --> 00:07:13,599
Why would my brother and Yujun hyung be dating?

79
00:07:16,227 --> 00:07:17,812
I'm not in the mood for jokes.

80
00:07:18,271 --> 00:07:21,023
I just thought she might be curious about how her son is doing.

81
00:07:30,575 --> 00:07:33,953
Just think about me.

82
00:07:33,953 --> 00:07:36,914
Let's not bring other people into our relationship.

83
00:07:36,914 --> 00:07:37,290
Okay?

84
00:07:43,421 --> 00:07:45,590
Is something going on lately?

85
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:46,924
Are you just tired?

86
00:07:49,010 --> 00:07:50,428
Is there anything you want to eat?

87
00:07:50,428 --> 00:07:52,054
I'll make it for you tomorrow.

88
00:07:52,054 --> 00:07:54,182
Or do you need anything?

89
00:07:54,348 --> 00:07:57,393
Didn't you say you needed to change your laptop?

90
00:08:07,820 --> 00:08:10,072
I don't need anything.

91
00:08:16,162 --> 00:08:18,998
You can do everything for me...

92
00:08:18,998 --> 00:08:21,834
...but I have nothing to give you.

93
00:08:22,418 --> 00:08:25,046
So maybe now...

94
00:08:25,046 --> 00:08:27,298
...should we just stop?

95
00:09:35,241 --> 00:09:39,287
Don't even think about running away.

96
00:09:39,287 --> 00:09:42,498
I know what you're thinking, but...

97
00:09:44,083 --> 00:09:48,087
...I can't let you go.

98
00:09:48,087 --> 00:09:53,676
You'll get used to it soon as time passes.

99
00:09:53,676 --> 00:09:57,263
To protect my world...

100
00:09:58,347 --> 00:10:00,975
...I absolutely need you, Yujun.
